ENTRY       EC 2.4.1.67                 Enzyme
NAME        galactinol---raffinose galactosyltransferase;
            galactinol-raffinose galactosyltransferase;
            stachyose synthetase;
            alpha-D-galactosyl-(1->3)-myo-inositol:raffinose galactosyltransferase
CLASS       Transferases;
            Glycosyltransferases;
            Hexosyltransferases
SYSNAME     alpha-D-galactosyl-(1->3)-1D-myo-inositol:raffinose galactosyltransferase
REACTION    alpha-D-galactosyl-(1->3)-1D-myo-inositol + raffinose = myo-inositol + stachyose [RN:R03418 R06042]
ALL_REAC    R03418 R06042(G)
SUBSTRATE   alpha-D-galactosyl-(1->3)-1D-myo-inositol [CPD:C01235];
            raffinose [CPD:C00492]
PRODUCT     myo-inositol [CPD:C00137];
            stachyose [CPD:C01613]
COMMENT     This enzyme also catalyses galactosyl transfer from stachyose to raffinose (shown by labelling) [4]. For synthesis of the substrate, see EC 2.4.1.123, inositol 3-alpha-galactosyltransferase. See also EC 2.4.1.82, galactinol---sucrose galactosyltransferase.
